    Storyblocks Licensing

    Simplified licensing done right. Thats royalty-free assets, yours forever (even if you decide to end your membership).

    Individuals

    For the freelancers, hobbyists, and YouTube aficionados.

    With our standard license, all your downloads are licensed to you. And you get covered by up to $20,000 indemnification.

    Businesses

    For marketing teams, broadcasters, and production houses.

    The Enterprise License is written directly to your organization, not the individual person, so youll feel covered no matter what you download. Plus, our business license offers your org with up to $1M in indemnification.
